Menu Structure
--------------

* Single Player
  - Quick Match
  - Custom Match
* Multiplayer
  - LIVE
    + Create Match
    + Join Match
  - System Link
    + Create Match
    + Join Match
* Awardments
* Help & Options
  - How to Play
  - Controls
    + A to select then move/attack
    + B to cancel selection
    + X to place a piece
    + Start to open menu
  - Options
    + Music on/off
    + Sound on/off
    + Change storage device
* Get Full Version
* Exit to Dashboard

